<p><strong>Sympathico is a theme suitable for all type of business, a friendly Premium WordPress Theme and very easy to use.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Slider</strong> – This Premium WordPress Theme comes with an impressive jQuery slider that can be used for each individual page, post and portfolio project. Every slider will have different images, and you can add up to 5 images for every slider + caption and link for every image.</p>
<p><strong>Custom Backgrounds</strong> – Sympathico allows you to add a custom background image for each individual page, post and portfolio project, it dosen’t matter the size of the image you add</p>
<p><strong>Contact and Comments</strong> – Both forms comes with and impressive jQuery validation , check out the comments.</p>
<p><strong>Logo</strong> – I know how important is the logo, so with Sympathico, your logo can have any size, it dosen’t matter, how small or big is your logo, you’ll see that your logo will fit with the theme, if you need to change the width or the hight, and give it more margin, everything will be done from Theme Option.</p>
<p><strong>Layout</strong> – From Theme Options ( a new one ) you can choose your layout Wide or Boxed, and ofcouse a lot more, you can play with the 6 predefined skins, choose a pattern from 18, or you can add your own pattern or background, it’s up to you, you can create your own skin ( unlimited colors ), or you can paste some custom style.</p>
<p><strong>HTML5 + CSS3 </strong>– Modern design with modern HTML5 tags, it is compatible with all major browsers.</p>
<p><strong>SEO </strong>– The main content block is placed before the sidebar, so will be crawled first by the search engines. All tags have been used properly for images, headings and so on. A sitemap is used for the theme ( and will be more easy for the search engines to index all the posts ), and for every page, post and portfolio project is assigned the H1 tag.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
