<p>Theme uses <strong>unique rounded images on blog and service boxes</strong>. Precise and user friendly admin panel allows you to do a lot of customizations without knowing any HTML or CSS . Colors, images, fonts, widgets, sliders, portfolios, galleries,&#8230; everything can be customized and configured via admin panel.</p>
<p>Theme is built on our robust MVC framework that means that HTML design is completely separated from other PHP ! Making updates cannot be easier. Template &amp; MVC framework will be under continuous improvement. Purchase the theme and get all updates for free.</p>
<p>Freestyle WordPress Theme comes also with customer support and after purchase service. We’ll do our best to answer all of your questions in a professional manner. Purchase this theme with confidence knowing that we’ll always be here to answer all of your questions.</p>
